-- models/stage/stg_user_info.sql
--sql
/*
with t as (
SELECT user_id, count(*) as nb
FROM default.user_info 
where user_id is not null
GROUP BY user_id
)
SELECT
  t.user_id,
  user_name,
  register_time,
  gender,
  city
FROM t
inner join default.user_info u
on t.user_id = u.user_id
and t.nb=1
*/

with not_null as (
select *
FROM default.user_info 
minus
select *
FROM default_dbt_test__audit.source_not_null_ecommerce_user_info_user_id 
) 
select n.*
from not_null n
left join default_dbt_test__audit.source_unique_ecommerce_user_info_user_id u
on n.user_id = u.unique_field
where u.unique_field is null

-- models/stage/stg_order_detail.sql
SELECT
  order_id,
  user_id,
  order_time,
  order_amount,
  pay_status
FROM default.order_detail

with transactions as (
    select 1 as tx_id, 101 as user_id, cast('2024-09-01' as date)  as tx_date, 100.00 as amount, 'deposit'  as tx_type
    union all
    select 2, 101, cast('2024-09-05' as date) , -30.00, 'withdraw'
    union all
    select 3, 102, cast('2024-09-06' as date) , 200.00, 'deposit'
    union all
    select 4, 101, cast('2024-09-10' as date), -50.00, 'withdraw'
    union all
    select 5, 103, cast('2024-09-10' as date), 500.00, 'deposit'
    union all
    select 5, 104, cast('2024-09-10' as date), -30.00, 'withdraw'
)

select *
from transactions

-- models/reject/stg_user_info_rejected.sql

select n.*,
      'source_not_null_ecommerce_user_info_user_id' as dq_rule
from default_dbt_test__audit.source_not_null_ecommerce_user_info_user_id n
union
select n.*,
  'source_unique_ecommerce_user_info_user_id' as dq_rule
from default.user_info n
inner join default_dbt_test__audit.source_unique_ecommerce_user_info_user_id u
on n.user_id = u.unique_field

select user_id
from default.user_info
where user_id is null

select
    user_id as unique_field,
    count(*) as n_records

from default.user_info
where user_id is not null
group by user_id
having count(*) > 1

-- models/mart/mart_user_order_summary.sql

SELECT
  u.user_id,
  u.user_name,
  u.register_time,
  u.city,
  COUNT(o.order_id) AS total_order_count,  
  SUM(o.order_amount) AS total_spend_amount,  
  MIN(o.order_time) AS first_order_time,  
  MAX(o.order_time) AS last_order_time  
FROM default.stg_user_info u  
LEFT JOIN default.stg_order_detail o 
  ON u.user_id = o.user_id
  AND o.pay_status = 'OK'  
GROUP BY
  u.user_id,
  u.user_name,
  u.register_time,
  u.city

-- 基于交易流水聚合用户余额
with base as (
    select *
    from default_gold.silver_transaction
),
user_balance as (
    select
        user_id,
        sum(amount) as balance,
        count(*) as tx_count,
        max(tx_date) as last_tx_date
    from base
    group by user_id
)

select *
from user_balance
